The paper describes the conversion process of a thesaurus into a SKOS format, which is relevant for information retrieval and search term recommendation. This involves analyzing the original dataset, mapping to SKOS classes and properties, and defining extensions based on SKOS-XL. These topics are related to information retrieval, artificial intelligence, machine learning, and databases, which are covered by the sub-categories cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DL, cs.LG, and cs.DB.
